OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, It will be easier to prosecute people  
OL,6, for sharing so-called revenge porn     
OL,7, after a change in the law in England   
OL,8, and Wales.                             
OL,10,FAmendments to the Online Safety Bill   
OL,11,Fbeing tabled on Tuesday will remove the
OL,12,Frequirement for prosecutors to prove   
OL,13,Fperpetrators intended to cause distress
OL,14,Fto secure a conviction.                
OL,16,FSharing deepfake porn is also being    
OL,17,Fcriminalised for the first time.       
OL,19,FBoth offences will be punishable by up 
OL,20,Fto six months in prison.               
